## Independent Services and Consulting

This license does not restrict individuals or organizations
from offering paid services related to setup, configuration,
hosting, or administration of servers that use Coffer.

Such services MUST be independent.

No person or entity may:

- claim to represent Coffer officially,
- imply endorsement, partnership, or affiliation,
- present paid services as “official” Coffer offerings.

You may sell your time.
You may not sell Coffer.

